Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.40,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HD24327&}胸が張り裂けそうで\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}悲痛欲绝仿佛胸口要裂开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.72,UTA,,0,0,0,,私のことが好きなら\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}如果喜欢我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.92,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H4BE0B4&}アノコを忘れて\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}就忘掉那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:40.12,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H4BE0B4&}どこか遠くへ連れて行って\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}带着我去远方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.92,UTA,,0,0,0,,はしゃぎたい人あつまれ\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}想要欢闹的人聚集于此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.52,UTA,,0,0,0,,夢見たい人歓迎\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}欢迎乐于做梦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:50.00,UTA,,0,0,0,,がんばるわたし達はいつだって\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}努力的我们无论何时都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.88,UTA,,0,0,0,,PRETTY DREAMER\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}PRETTY DREAMER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.96,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H765BEA&}未来行きパスポートの\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}不要忘记更新
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.52,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC58B78&}更新は忘れずに\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}前往未来的护照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:13.76,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HB9AD01&}最新の今が退屈じゃ違うでしょ？\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}最新的现在很无聊 这不太对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.48,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HA86C7E&}日常が冒険だね\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}日常的每一天都是冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.24,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HA87872&}ワクワクのキミがリーダー\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}兴奋不已的你是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.48,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HB9AD01&}こっちまで一緒になって\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}到这边也是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.44,UTA,,0,0,0,,ハジケちゃうよ\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}欢闹起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:29.56,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H765BEA&}みんなで乗り込んじゃえ\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}大家一起进入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:34.16,UTA,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HB9AD01&}毎日がパーティー気分で\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}{\1c&HC58B78&}每天都像是派对一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.44,UTA,,0,0,0,,ハイテンション！\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}情绪高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.48,UTA,,0,0,0,,(YES! YES! YES!)\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}(YES! YES! YES!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.84,UTA,,0,0,0,,反則的にたのしい\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}犯规一样的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.44,UTA,,0,0,0,,もう感動級に笑っちゃう\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}已是感动级别的欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:44.28,UTA,,0,0,0,,ねえこんな気が合うなんて\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}呐 如此合拍的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.52,UTA,,0,0,0,,そうそうないよね\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.36,UTA,,0,0,0,,圧倒的にうれしい\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}压倒性的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.08,UTA,,0,0,0,,もう友情なんだありがとう\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}已是友情非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.32,UTA,,0,0,0,,つないだ絆で光れ！\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}我们之间的联系闪耀光芒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.36,UTA,,0,0,0,,(Let's shine!!)\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}(Let's shine!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.96,UTA,,0,0,0,,自分色に\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}以自己的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.68,UTA,,0,0,0,,はしゃぎたい人あつまれ\N{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Bold}想要欢闹的人聚集于此
